40:02.444 --> 40:06.031
Sorry, someone who
doesn't want me to feel shit

40:06.114 --> 40:08.283
about myself is finally calling me back.

40:09.368 --> 40:10.827
Matt, is that you?

40:10.911 --> 40:12.621
Oh, no, you're right here.

40:13.121 --> 40:15.832
-Sorry, I've been working, like--
-All day?

40:15.916 --> 40:18.001
Who needs to hear that much bass?

40:18.085 --> 40:21.046
No, my day job.
I was gonna call you. I just didn't…

40:21.129 --> 40:22.631
Well, now you don't have to.

40:24.383 --> 40:25.759
I hope you score with your date.

40:25.843 --> 40:27.928
-Oh, no. That's my brother.
-Sure.

40:28.011 --> 40:29.596
No, we have different mothers.

40:39.857 --> 40:41.567
These are from that lad over there.

40:42.484 --> 40:44.444
Make sure you give him a nice "thank you."

41:05.215 --> 41:06.508
Hello?

41:06.592 --> 41:07.968
Hey, how are you? It's Matt.

41:08.677 --> 41:09.887
That wasn't so hard, was it?

41:11.763 --> 41:13.473
You said something about getting dinner?

41:13.974 --> 41:17.269
Yeah, I know what I said,
but what do you have to say?

41:17.352 --> 41:21.231
I say maybe let's get a Chinese sometime?

41:21.315 --> 41:24.484
Well, we only have
one Chinese restaurant in town,

41:24.568 --> 41:26.278
and I'm banned from it, so…

41:26.820 --> 41:29.281
How do you get banned
from a Chinese restaurant?

41:30.365 --> 41:31.450
Break up with the owner?

41:32.951 --> 41:33.952
Oh, right.

41:34.036 --> 41:36.830
Well, I really fancy Chinese,

41:36.914 --> 41:40.667
so if you two could get back together,
maybe that would be quite convenient.

41:42.628 --> 41:43.962
What are you up to anyway?

41:45.047 --> 41:46.924
I'm just talking to you.

42:21.834 --> 42:23.085
You're early.

42:24.545 --> 42:27.923
Yeah, well. Early bird.

42:30.342 --> 42:31.718
Can we stop for sandwiches?

42:46.066 --> 42:47.943
-Oh, for Christ's sake.
-Do you wanna drive?

42:51.655 --> 42:54.408
It's just nerves. Okay?

42:55.200 --> 42:56.493
Let's try this again.

43:22.769 --> 43:23.770
Need a hand?

43:23.854 --> 43:26.315
-No, I'll manage. Would you stop--
-All right.

43:26.982 --> 43:28.901
Come on, John Paul. Hurry up.

43:31.945 --> 43:33.864
Will you wait for me please?

43:48.879 --> 43:49.922
Christ!

44:27.251 --> 44:31.547
If the box is empty, Grace,
throw the damn thing away.

44:31.630 --> 44:33.590
I've said it a hundred times.

44:38.136 --> 44:39.513
Oh, for Christ's sake.

44:42.266 --> 44:43.976
What on earth?

45:07.374 --> 45:10.961
This is unbelievable. How did you--

45:12.462 --> 45:14.882
Mam.

45:16.800 --> 45:18.135
Mam!

45:18.218 --> 45:20.846
No, you're right. I won't do that.
Yeah, come on.

45:38.822 --> 45:41.074
Oh, Mam, please don't.
She's about to start. Please.

45:42.034 --> 45:43.952
Hey, love. Everything okay?

45:44.036 --> 45:45.704
Mammy, my feet are so blistered,

45:45.787 --> 45:48.165
all my skin came off in my socks.

45:48.707 --> 45:51.168
And I've been tearing
the place apart for plasters.

45:53.045 --> 45:54.129
Where the hell are you?

45:54.213 --> 45:56.840
We're-- Look, this is--

45:56.924 --> 45:58.425
I promise it's nothing
to be concerned about.

45:58.509 --> 46:00.260
I just had this crazy idea.

46:00.344 --> 46:01.553
Where are you?

46:03.931 --> 46:07.476
B and I got tickets
to a Lizzo concert in Dublin.

46:08.268 --> 46:10.395
Are you kidding?

46:10.479 --> 46:14.399
No. They're a gift from Eva.

46:18.820 --> 46:20.739
We'll talk about it when I get home,
Grace.

46:20.822 --> 46:24.368
Good evening, Dublin!

46:24.451 --> 46:26.286
Blanaid?

46:28.747 --> 46:31.083
Bloody Garveys.

46:47.891 --> 46:49.685
I'm hungry. You?

46:51.478 --> 46:52.521
No.

47:37.608 --> 47:39.443
Been an hour since the lights went out.

47:39.526 --> 47:40.986
He's gotta be asleep by now.

47:44.281 --> 47:45.282
Okay.

48:05.177 --> 48:07.221
Are you gonna join me, or just sit there?

48:08.472 --> 48:09.723
I think maybe the latter.

48:10.349 --> 48:12.142
Which one's the latter?
I always get those confused.

48:12.226 --> 48:14.228
I can't do it, Bibi. I can't do it.

48:14.311 --> 48:17.564
-Eva, you said you were fine.
-How do I know if I'm fine or not?

48:19.191 --> 48:22.152
I mean, look at us!
What are we even doing here?

48:22.236 --> 48:24.154
You know the answer to that question.

48:26.156 --> 48:28.408
All right then. Just gonna do it alone.

48:38.544 --> 48:40.462
Are you actually
gonna let me do this on my own?

48:40.546 --> 48:43.006
I don't want you to do this at all.

49:16.582 --> 49:18.250
Frigid bitch.

49:20.544 --> 49:22.129
Come on.

49:36.643 --> 49:38.812
-Jesus Christ!
-Fuck!

49:40.230 --> 49:41.231
What's taking you so long?

49:41.315 --> 49:43.859
What's taking me so long?
Are you bored out there?

49:43.942 --> 49:45.569
I was worried about you.

49:45.652 --> 49:47.863
The matches won't light.
Give me your lighter.

49:47.946 --> 49:49.907
-What?
-Your cigarettes.

49:50.490 --> 49:52.618
-I threw them away.
-Why would you do that?

49:52.701 --> 49:54.536
Will you just calm down?

50:10.511 --> 50:11.512
Wait.

50:21.438 --> 50:22.731
No, wait. Wait.

50:25.150 --> 50:26.151
I need to finish this.

50:37.079 --> 50:38.497
Go!

51:01.270 --> 51:03.021
Shit, your phone. Turn it off!

51:05.065 --> 51:06.191
Why's he calling me?

51:29.089 --> 51:32.384
-What the actual fuck?
-What?

51:32.467 --> 51:33.886
Oh, my God. He's over there!

51:33.969 --> 51:36.763
-Why?
-He's over there! Fuck!

51:36.847 --> 51:41.935
No!

51:44.104 --> 51:48.901
No!
